title: UI update checkpoint 2.
message:
UI update checkpoint 2.
Now running in fragments! so switching modes will not turn off the
light and switching is much faster. This might be the build
for GB devices, because I'm scared about trying to handle the camera
from a service on some GB devices.

title: UI update checkpoint. Not ready for release.
message:
UI update checkpoint. Not ready for release.
Add dialog for switching mode, add support library, add light switch widget.
Currently tested only on JB, but should still be compatible with Froyo.
Next step is to migrate UI components to fragments for seamless mode changes
that does not turn the light off and on... then a Service for widget support.
